@endpoint = http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}/api/admin/user

### 404
GET {{ endpoint }}/azertyuiop

### Get one user
GET {{ endpoint }}/1

### Get an user who does not exist
GET {{ endpoint }}/9999

### Get an user with an id as not a number
GET {{ endpoint }}/tartempion

